replaced a toilet in the past five years or so, you may look back
on your old toilets with nostalgia. The bodies of toilets available
for sale now are still as tough as nails, but they may not function
with the effortless grace of their ancestors. But if you really
want to replace a toilet now, it's a job most average
do-it-yourselfers can handle. (Cummings, Dayton Daily News)
