<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-15 13:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7980 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      10-15 0906
</HEADER>
<BODY>
 AM-NYT-BUDGET  
<TEXT>
<P>
   (lh) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FOR SATURDAY AMS &LR;
</P>
<P>
