   SPORTS (``s'' category)
</P>
<P>
   BBN-NL (New York) _ Full coverage of Game 3 of the National
League Championship Series between the Atlanta Braves and New York
Mets. The Braves carry a 2-0 lead in the best-of-seven series. By
CARLTON THOMPSON.
</P>
<P>
   With: BBN-ROBERTSON-COLUMN
</P>
<P>
   BBA-AL (Boston) _ The best pitcher in baseball over the past
decade, Roger Clemens, will go head-to-head against the best
pitcher in baseball this year, Pedro Martinez, on Saturday
afternoon at Fenway Park in Game 3 of the American League
Championship Series. New York leads the best-of-seven series 2-0.
By JOSEPH DUARTE.
</P>
