them part of the military chain of command. At the same time the
new military command is a public acknowledgment that as the worlds
most technically advanced nation, the U.S. is also potentially the
most vulnerable to foreign cyberthreats. By John Markoff.
</P>
<P>
   MATHEMATICS-REVIEW (Undated) _ There is no Nobel prize in
