   MUNCHKIN-SUIT (Los Angeles) _ Munchkin Inc., a producer of baby
products, has withdrawn its patent infringement lawsuit against
rival Luv N' Care Inc. of in Monroe, La.Now Luv N' Care may counter
sue Munchkin for unspecified damages because several big clients,
including Wal-Mart, stopped ordering products because of the flap.
By Dave Wilcox. (Will move in the ``f'' financial news file.)
</P>
